ement elementor-element-9649de4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9649de4\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2caeddc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2caeddc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong data-start=\"130\" data-end=\"143\">Industry:<\/strong> Food &amp; Confectionery<br data-start=\"164\" data-end=\"167\" \/><strong data-start=\"167\" data-end=\"184\">Company Size:<\/strong> 100,000+ employees | 300+ sites | $35B+ annual revenue<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51eb4cb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"51eb4cb\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fa268e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4fa268e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About This Case Study<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f82402d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f82402d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c81691 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1c81691\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This case study explores how a leading global food and confectionery manufacturer transformed its master data management (MDM) strategy with Verdantis. With operations spanning 75+ countries and 300+ sites, the company faced challenges related to data silos, inconsistencies, and high manual intervention costs. By implementing Verdantis\u2019 AI-powered MDM solution, they achieved cleaner, standardized, and more accessible data, leading to improved efficiency, reduced costs, and smarter decision-making.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4cab62b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4cab62b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7fb92a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7fb92a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Requirements Addressed<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-23e9de2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"23e9de2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b261ae0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b261ae0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong data-start=\"573\" data-end=\"608\">&#8211; Data Complexity &amp; Fragmentation<\/strong> \u2013 Multiple SAP instances, different taxonomies, and 10+ languages led to inefficiencies.<\/p><p><strong data-start=\"702\" data-end=\"735\">&#8211; Duplicate &amp; Inconsistent Data<\/strong> \u2013 Supplier and product records were duplicated across regions, causing procurement errors.<\/p><p><strong data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"858\">&#8211; Lack of Data Governance<\/strong> \u2013 Inconsistent data entry and manual intervention resulted in unreliable reporting.<\/p><p><strong data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"973\">&#8211; High Operational Costs<\/strong> \u2013 Manual data cleansing and consolidation were time-consuming and expensive.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-833dc94 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"833dc94\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f6c3fdf elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f6c3fdf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Download This Case Study?<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-22fd1a4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"22fd1a4\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0babd4b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0babd4b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>&#8211; Learn how AI-powered MDM eliminates data silos and inconsistencies<\/p><p>&#8211;\u00a0See how automation reduces manual intervention by 80 percent<\/p><p>&#8211; Discover how a global enterprise achieved real-time, accurate reporting<\/p><p>&#8211; Understand the impact of data governance on procurement and inventory management<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba2f11b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ba2f11b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n